channel.title: Interior Design Masters
channel.desc: The designers head to Allianz Stadium Twickenham, the iconic home of England rugby, to do up hospitality suites. They must create a premium experience for diehard rugby fans by producing a swanky bar for serving pre-match drinks and a stylish dining area for putting on a generous spread. Restaurateur Nisha Katona helps Michelle decide who will win a place in the quarter-final.
